{"title_page": "Shift (The Living End album)", "text_new": "{{more citations needed|date=May 2016}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2016}}\n{{Use Australian English|date=May 2016}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Shift\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[The Living End]]\n| cover      = The_Living_End_Shift_Cover500px.jpg\n| border     = yes\n| alt        = The Living End - Shift\n| released   = 13 May 2016\n| recorded   = Red Door Sounds, [[Melbourne, Australia]]<br><small>Red Door Sounds & Filthy Fidgets Studio, [[Los Angeles, California]] 'Keep On Running'</small>\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Alternative Rock]]\n| length     = {{Duration|m=39}}\n| label      = [[Dew Process]]\n| producer   = Paul 'Woody' Annison & Chris Cheney<br><small>Paul 'Woody' Annison, Chris Cheney and Filthy Fidgets '<i>Keep On Running</i>'<br><small>Paul 'Woody' Annison & The Living End '<i>One Step</i>', '<i>With Enemies Like That</i>'\n| prev_title = [[The Ending Is Just the Beginning Repeating]]\n| prev_year  = 2011\n| next_title = [[Wunderbar_(The_Living_End_album)|Wunderbar]]\n| next_year  = 2018\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Shift\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = Monkey\n | single1date = 21 March 2016\n | single2     = Keep On Running\n | single2date = 21 March 2016\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Shift''' is the seventh studio album by Australian [[punk rock]] band [[The Living End]].  It was produced by Woody Annison<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.enmoretheatre.com.au/events/2016/06/11/the-living-end|title=THE LIVING END {{!}} Enmore Theatre|website=www.enmoretheatre.com.au|access-date=2016-05-15}}</ref> and recorded at Red Door Sounds<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://crucialmusic.com.au/news/red-door-sounds/|title=Red Door Sounds \u00ab  Crucial Music|website=crucialmusic.com.au|access-date=2016-05-15}}</ref> in [[Melbourne]], Australia.\n\n==Track listing==\nSongs and lyrics by [[Chris Cheney]], music by [[The Living End]] except where noted.\n\n{{Track list